description:
After some with hiccups with the night vision gear in the last installment, this time the Midnight Takedown crew have hit the nail on the head!
Peter has chosen long time pro Mark Davis, as well as Mr. Pete, to join him on an adrenaline-filled trip to surprise Jade Marxxx, who sleeps deeply, completely isolated in the Armory basement. Jade gets the intense experience she signed up for, and more...
Much hardcore fucking, bondage, and sensory overload take place in this fast-paced installment!
title: Midnight Takedown 3
